{"tid":381514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人唔寵得！","createTime":"2017-08-31T04:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:27:36.000Z","uid":142103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f5d5e4ef2e941456088ab0c6f28728a6f785ab","tid":381514,"uid":142103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"上星期同條女分手，係佢提出<br />\n我一直都好寵佢，<br />\n有咩都就曬佢，<br />\n間中俾下驚喜佢，<br />\n佢想做咩都支持佢。。。<br />\n就係咁，<br />\n有一次，佢話想做組媽，我其實<strong>唔</strong>鐘意！<br />\n但我知佢好想去！<br />\n我支持左佢去💩<br />\n佢知我唔鐘意，所以佢同我講！<br />\n「放心啦，無事既！我咁愛你」<br />\n嗯！我信左！！！！<br />\n佢入camp冇點覆我，都算<br />\n有野做緊喎，忙喎<br />\n<br />\n但去到上星期，佢同我講分手<br />\n我仲一心諗住我問題<br />\n我今日終於知道，原來佢鐘意左camp入面其中一個男仔，所以飛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以女人未到八十歲都唔可以俾飽飯佢食係真<br />\n佢地唔識珍惜<br />\n寵得既都冇好結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb874f8a7b057ad1e3d6d46bb86fc29fd31f05b","tid":381514,"uid":5806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"放心 佢會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec993e43b68a605f9e2e429d7cfba1a17c2221d","tid":381514,"uid":142103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心 佢會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢後悔都太遲，我已經因愛成恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdeee14143d7957c8edda8aadbd14a0b25bd9d6","tid":381514,"uid":31749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82f9d4e61b5c841892e8855e87869c889950811f","tid":381514,"uid":93200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"女人話變就變 因為佢覺得你對佢好係理所當然"},{"pid":"20e32563c20b45a55dc3217d4ce514b2acec8e7e","tid":381514,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"有冇屌到，有冇閃卡"},{"pid":"5552eaed8e09dc4eeb2f9272a023889e3670fbd8","tid":381514,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"一齊咗幾耐？中出過未？"},{"pid":"fe1c37f1d847830690f35fd66e3fb535aa69a246","tid":381514,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}